name: CELESTIAL MOON w/ CRYSTALS & ROSES 12oz travel tumbler
description:
Keeping your drinks cold has never been this spiritually cool. Our gorgeous, high quality CELESTIAL MOON w/ CRYSTALS & ROSES 12oz travel tumblers are designed with double wall vacuum insulation to keep your hot drinks warm for up to five hours and cold drinks cold for up to 12 hours. The durable stainless steel outside keeps condensation away, so you can use them for both hot and cold drinks without the need to ‘sweat’ over what’s on your cup. Plus, they come with an easy-to-use lid that’s straw friendly, so you can sip without the hassle of removing it each time!
handmade to order in ❤california❤
